In order to compile bubblegum, you need the following libraries and their -dev
or -devel part:

- libgtkglext1
- libfreetype
- libsdl-image
- libfxt (available on cvs -d :pserver:anonymous@cvs.sv.gnu.org:/sources/fkt co FxT )

You also need the "bubblelib" and "bubbles" modules and their dependencies.
